&lt;p&gt;An exciting opportunity has arisen for a p&lt;strong&gt;art -time&lt;/strong&gt; Practice Nurse to come and join our team at our Windsor town centre based surgery.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;You will be responsible for promoting patient self-care and providing safe and high quality nursing care to our 10,500 registered patients.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;It is essential you have experience within a primary care setting and qualifications in Long Term Conditions such as Diabetes and COPD.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We are looking for 2/3 days per week.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;If you are looking to join a forward thinking and aspirational practice we would love to hear from you.&lt;/p&gt;
